{"tid":32284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本妹「穿越」700年 竟同元朝皇后撞臉","createTime":"2016-12-10T06:00:12.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T21:14:05.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9e5fcc30b78bc28398f0526f0f9b6d694089bd86","tid":32284,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:00:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://simg314.magcasa.com/content_images/2016/12/07/457354/1481109325_4151.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsimg314.magcasa.com%2Fcontent_images%2F2016%2F12%2F07%2F457354%2F1481109325_4151.jpg&h=fc5110da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n莫非真的有輪迴轉世！最近有一名日本女生，到台灣遊學，期間遊覽台北故宮，竟找到自己的「前前前世」。這名日本女生當時正在觀看一個有關元朝公主畫像展覽，其中一幅有&amp;#30528;大餅臉的元朝皇后畫像，居然跟她「長相一模一樣」，讓她笑說「這就是我的前前前世」。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，這名日本女生當時觀看的，正是「公主的雅集：蒙元皇室與書畫鑑藏文化」展覽，當中所展出多項蒙古公主祥哥剌吉的收藏，其中包括多幅元朝皇后的畫作。<br />\n<br />\n其中一幅皇后的畫作，竟與日本女生「撞臉」，同樣有大餅臉，單眼皮、鼻子與嘴巴都十分相似。日本女生也忍不住與「畫像」自拍，放上twitter後，令上萬日本網友推爆，驚呼「也太像了吧」、「真的是前前前世無誤」、「有種命中註定遇到前世的感覺」。<br />\n<br />\n東森新聞"},{"pid":"07979c2f015f9b070aa5a4b1f8bce17d6ed941ba","tid":32284,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:03:06.000Z","msg":"古代美女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f8496aea81070e1a88080abaa0251aa42b04a1","tid":32284,"uid":59839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:05:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387f797663137926442ef4b93f0677813736da8f","tid":32284,"uid":92,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:07:06.000Z","msg":"好樣衰"},{"pid":"fc97e2503debc8cf641cd2e04fde2fd393cafea3","tid":32284,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:07:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe51504124e7d100f1d82f04b858aa8a8cc4505","tid":32284,"uid":89,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep